. For me the only way to fix this was to destroy both stellar and iScroll and restart them:

``` JavaScript
// Destroy
iScrollInstance.destroy();
$('#scroller').stellar('destroy');

// Restart
iScrollInstance = new iScroll('wrapper');
iOSStellar();
```

(iScrollInstance is a global var)
